msgid "Build, verify, sign, and publish a Klein for Ray release."
msgstr "构建、验证、签名并发布 Klein for Ray 版本。"

msgid "Release process"
msgstr "发布流程"

msgid ""
"Confirm CI, dependency review, CodeQL, package checks, and the full "
"integration suite are green on the release commit."
msgstr "确认发布提交上的 CI、依赖审查、CodeQL、包检查和完整集成测试套件均已通过。"

msgid "Update `CHANGELOG.md`, package version, and `CITATION.cff`."
msgstr "更新 `CHANGELOG.md`、包版本和 `CITATION.cff`。"

msgid ""
"Build with `python -m build` and inspect both archives for `LICENSE`, "
"`NOTICE`, expected package data, and absence of credentials or private "
"endpoints."
msgstr "使用 `python -m build` 构建，并检查两个归档是否包含 `LICENSE`、`NOTICE` 和预期的包数据，且不含凭据或私有端点。"

msgid ""
"Run `python -m twine check dist/*` and install the wheel in a clean "
"environment."
msgstr "运行 `python -m twine check dist/*`，并在干净环境中安装 wheel。"

msgid ""
"Create a signed `vX.Y.Z` tag. The release workflow publishes through PyPI "
"Trusted Publishing; long-lived PyPI tokens are not used."
msgstr "创建已签名的 `vX.Y.Z` 标签。发布工作流通过 PyPI Trusted Publishing 发布，不使用长期有效的 PyPI 令牌。"

msgid ""
"Publish GitHub release notes and verify the PyPI provenance attestation."
msgstr "发布 GitHub 发行说明，并验证 PyPI 来源证明。"

msgid ""
"Do not publish from an unclean worktree or reuse a version already uploaded "
"to PyPI. Test releases should use a PEP 440 pre-release version."
msgstr "不要从不干净的工作树发布，也不要复用已上传至 PyPI 的版本。测试版本应使用符合 PEP 440 的预发布版本号。"

msgid "Build with `python -m build`, run `python scripts/check_distribution.py dist/*`, and inspect both archives for `LICENSE`, `NOTICE`, expected package data, and absence of credentials, workflows, caches, or private endpoints."
msgstr "使用 `python -m build` 构建，运行 `python scripts/check_distribution.py dist/*`，并检查两种归档均包含 `LICENSE`、`NOTICE` 和预期的包数据，同时不包含凭据、工作流、缓存或私有端点。"

msgid "Verify the CycloneDX SBOM, `SHA256SUMS`, GitHub build-provenance attestation, immutable GitHub release assets, and PyPI Trusted Publisher provenance."
msgstr "验证 CycloneDX SBOM、`SHA256SUMS`、GitHub 构建来源证明、不可变的 GitHub Release 资产以及 PyPI Trusted Publisher 来源信息。"
